import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import App from './App'
import { BrowserRouter,Routes } from 'react-router-dom'

const AppWithRouter = () => (
  <BrowserRouter>
  <Routes>
    <App />
    </Routes>
  </BrowserRouter>
)

ReactDOM.render(<AppWithRouter />, document.getElementById('root'))
